{"tid":1266634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明白大家睇到第三個人嘅事情緒可能好差，試下搵身邊嘅人傾下或者搵嘢減壓","createTime":"2019-06-29T15:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T15:13:16.000Z","uid":213018,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c24e8e36b14f4c84ef1de9b5a98a5dd5ca0ba542","tid":1266634,"uid":213018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:01:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">利申非專業人士</span><br />\n我都有相同諗法<br />\n人都有極限<br />\n要識得搵地方講自己嘅心聲<br />\n咁樣人地先可以入到你個心幫你舒困<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前面是絕路<br />\n希望在轉角<br />\n你唔係得自己一個<br />\n有好多人開心陪你笑<br />\n難過陪您喊<br />\n一齊食椒<br />\n一齊食彈<br />\n我唔知點樣情緒輔導你<br />\n但我會有耐性去聽<br />\n歡迎係下面留言</span></span>"},{"pid":"2f9565091db9a8c471bf0f58963d51c227ffec86","tid":1266634,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:01:58.000Z","msg":"[長文]求下大家唔好自殺，有梁先生真係夠啦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1266479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1266479</a>"},{"pid":"a82b8e17ee1a5368995b993844e2948555ab52d0","tid":1266634,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:02:40.000Z","msg":"［小心五毛分化放負撚］無力感元凶係政府同保皇黨，並非源自抗爭手法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1266581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1266581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c9d2e282edf2202c280c3b3b9d3ff86bacb9aad0","tid":1266634,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>知道手足你地嘅情緒，大家都好唔開心，有情緒可以搵我地傾訴下。<br />\n網站聊天室：<a href=\"http://nitecat.bgca.org.hk/tc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnitecat.bgca.org.hk%2Ftc%2F&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo4CLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=8fc1f92d\" target=\"_blank\">http://nitecat.bgca.org.hk/tc/</a><br />\nWhatsApp：9726 8159 / 9852 8625<br />\nTg：<a href=\"https://t.me/nitecattbbg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2F